  "subject": "[CPS] Use default configuration for Kakfa",
  "commit_message": "[CPS] Use default configuration for Kakfa\n\nCreate kafka default configuration directly in the configuration file\ninstead of putting it in values.yaml.\nIt allows to generate secrets for the kafka login/password.\nConfiguration can still be fully overriden by using dedicated dict keys:\n\n- `config.eventPublisherOverride` for CPS Core\n- `config.eventConsumptionOverride` for CPS temporal\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-1\nSigned-off-by: Sylvain Desbureaux <sylvain.desbureaux@orange.com>\nChange-Id: I6c6c5598c1f681590f6c831e6334b2a5aaabee30\n",
